a-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 05, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104gkf1665702815102.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gkf1665702815102.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gkf1665702815102.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"gkf1665702815102\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Device Section\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The device section contains the general commands needed to drive the device.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"gkf1665702815102__topic_d63680e1_d63681e1_d63682e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gkf1665702815102__p_d63683e1_d63684e1_d63685e1\">Each definition can contain up to 1024 characters defining a function mapping using the following syntax:</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gkf1665702815102__p_d63686e1_d63687e1_d63688e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">begin_device</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gkf1665702815102__p_d63689e1_d63690e1_d63691e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">OutputSequence</var>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">UnifaceMnemonic</var> {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Description</var>}</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gkf1665702815102__p_d63692e1_d63693e1_d63694e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">end_device</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gkf1665702815102__section_e3t_bth_hcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d177530e81\">Delimiters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"gkf1665702815102__table_d5552e1_d5553e1_d5554e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"gkf1665702815102__table_d5552e1_d5553e1_d5554e1__entry__1\">Mnemonic </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"gkf1665702815102__table_d5552e1_d5553e1_d5554e1__entry__2\">Explanation </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gkf1665702815102__table_d5552e1_d5553e1_d5554e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">begin_device</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gkf1665702815102__table_d5552e1_d5553e1_d5554e1__entry__2\">Mark start of general device information.\n                     </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gkf1665702815102__table_d5552e1_d5553e1_d5554e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">end_device</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gkf1665702815102__table_d5552e1_d5553e1_d5554e1__entry__2\">Mark end of general device information.\n                     </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gkf1665702815102__section_ndk_dth_hcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d177530e140\">Arguments</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"gkf1665702815102__ul_hzg_3th_hcc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gkf1665702815102__li_d27773e1_d27774e1_d27775e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">OutputSequence</var>—sequence of\n               codes used by the device to perform the requested action. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gkf1665702815102__li_d27776e1_d27777e1_d27778e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">UnifaceMnemonic</var>—Uniface\n               mnemonic code recognized by the device translation table compiler. See <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hdh1665702981923.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hdh1665702981923.html\" title=\"Uniface uses a set of mnemonics to identify particular functions. When you define a device translation table, you define the device control codes that implement a particular function.\">Device Translation Table Mnemonics</a>. Some mnemonics include parameters in the output\n               sequence that can be used to determine layout and formatting information. See <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mzr1665702983304.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mzr1665702983304.html\" title=\"Some mnemonics include parameters in the output sequence that can be used to determine layout and formatting information, such as horizontal and vertical coordinates, numeric base zero (decimal, octal, or hexadecimal), zero padding, and so on. The output sequence can even include expressions that use the parameters incalculation, for example, to increment values.\">Parameters in the Output Sequence</a>. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gkf1665702815102__li_d27779e1_d27780e1_d27781e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Description</var>—optional\n               description or comments. Except for the <code class=\"ph codeph\">mode_</code> definitions, comments\n               are ignored by the device translation table compiler. </li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"gkf1665702815102__pre_enh_gth_hcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">^^ USYSTERM (VT220) device display and printer definitions table\nBEGIN_DEVICE  start of device section\nMeta_Western Display\n^esc= init select keypad\n^esc[1;24r close leave terminal in 'normal state'\n^esc[%v;%hH cursor(1,1) cursor posit command\n^esc[?3l mode_0(80,24) normal width dimension\n^esc[?3h mode_1(132,24) large width dimension\n^esc[2J clear_screen clear full screen\n^esc[%pX erase_line erase (part) of line function\n^esc[%v;%yr^esc[%v;%hH^escM scroll_down scroll lines down\n^esc[%v;%yr^esc[%y;%hH^escD scroll_up scroll lines up\n^esc[%v;%hH^esc[%p@ scroll_right scroll positions right\n^esc[%v;%hH^esc[%pP scroll_left scroll positions left\n^007 buzz ringbell command\n^FF formfeed print new page\n^CR return print eol\n^LF linefeed print advance\n^esc[0m novideo video attributes setting\n^esc[0;4m underscore\n^esc[0;7m inverse\n^esc[0;4;7m inv_und\n^esc[0;1m high\n^esc[0;4;1m hig_und\n^esc[0;7;1m hig_inv\n^esc[0;4;7;1m hig_inv_und\n^esc[0;5m blink\n^esc[0;4;5m bli_und\n^esc[0;7;5m bli_inv\n^esc[0;4;7;5m bli_inv_und\n^esc[0;1;5m bli_hig\n^esc[0;4;1;5m bli_hig_und\n^esc[0;7;1;5m bli_hig_inv\n^esc[0;4;7;1;5m bli_hig_inv_und\nEND_DEVICE\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527893\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527893\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Device Section Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 05, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Device Section The device section contains the general commands needed to drive the device. Each definition can contain up to 1024 characters defining a function mapping using the following syntax: begin_device OutputSequence UnifaceMnemonic { Description } end_device Delimiters Mnemonic Explanation begin_device Mark start of general device information. end_device Mark end of general device information. Arguments OutputSequence —sequence of codes used by the device to perform the requested action. UnifaceMnemonic —Uniface mnemonic code recognized by the device translation table compiler. See Device Translation Table Mnemonics . Some mnemonics include parameters in the output sequence that can be used to determine layout and formatting information. See Parameters in the Output Sequence . Description —optional description or comments. Except for the mode_ definitions, comments are ignored by the device translation table compiler. ^^ USYSTERM (VT220) device display and printer definitions table BEGIN_DEVICE start of device section Meta_Western Display ^esc= init select keypad ^esc[1;24r close leave terminal in 'normal state' ^esc[%v;%hH cursor(1,1) cursor posit command ^esc[?3l mode_0(80,24) normal width dimension ^esc[?3h mode_1(132,24) large width dimension ^esc[2J clear_screen clear full screen ^esc[%pX erase_line erase (part) of line function ^esc[%v;%yr^esc[%v;%hH^escM scroll_down scroll lines down ^esc[%v;%yr^esc[%y;%hH^escD scroll_up scroll lines up ^esc[%v;%hH^esc[%p@ scroll_right scroll positions right ^esc[%v;%hH^esc[%pP scroll_left scroll positions left ^007 buzz ringbell command ^FF formfeed print new page ^CR return print eol ^LF linefeed print advance ^esc[0m novideo video attributes setting ^esc[0;4m underscore ^esc[0;7m inverse ^esc[0;4;7m inv_und ^esc[0;1m high ^esc[0;4;1m hig_und ^esc[0;7;1m hig_inv ^esc[0;4;7;1m hig_inv_und ^esc[0;5m blink ^esc[0;4;5m bli_und ^esc[0;7;5m bli_inv ^esc[0;4;7;5m bli_inv_und ^esc[0;1;5m bli_hig ^esc[0;4;1;5m bli_hig_und ^esc[0;7;1;5m bli_hig_inv ^esc[0;4;7;1;5m bli_hig_inv_und END_DEVICE Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}